categories: Category:Imperial Navy officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: A female Imperial served as the commander of the starship Panaka as part of the Coruscant blockade in 5 ABY. When former 204th Imperial Fighter Wing leader Colonel Soran Keize traveled to Coruscant to destroy a data bank that cataloged the actions and profiles of every single Imperial, the female unsuccessfully attempted to stop Keize from reaching Coruscant.
